i kỳ 20 - 秦州雜詩其二十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Minh-Th%E1%BA%A7n/Th%C3%A1i-li%C3%AAn-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-fcr4U1HGb7Ypb2wT0zeqBw">Thái liên khúc kỳ 5 - 採蓮曲其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Minh-Th%E1%BA%A7n/author-YaMRkwvXgT5g5W4Ryp1GKA">Thẩm Minh Thần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quang-Du%E1%BA%ABn/Tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-08/poem-KyP9BZYiwuLA3BYAo6cN-Q">Trúc chi từ kỳ 08 - 竹枝詞其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quang-Du%E1%BA%ABn/author-o4EVPW8qBqGIiDBnjz0VQg">Vương Quang Duẫn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Trang/Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-d%E1%BA%A1-phi%E1%BA%BFm-chu-du-Nam-Kh%C3%AA/poem-tXyS5QdNOh84NhCDW5XoEg">Tuyết dạ phiếm chu du Nam Khê - 夜雪泛舟遊南溪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Trang/author-sRwDvUqTTXJgu1Qk5ewg6w">Vi Trang</a>)<br></div>	</div>
